{"tid":1961711,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳若希爆老公私密死撐好正常","createTime":"2020-04-07T03:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:44:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfafd75291303eb86ffcfbf79978881068dc9c26","tid":1961711,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"吳若希（Jinny）日前在網上直播時，大爆老公私密，由於涉及兒童不宜內容而遭網民狂轟。Jinny昨日到新城宣傳新歌，自言目標是做好宣傳，記者問到目標應否改為「收 把口」，不要再爆老公私隱時，她說：「我老公不介意喎！其實好正常 （指自慰），幾多歲呀？（唔怕教壞小朋友Fans？）我凌晨時分才開live，相信現在的小朋友不用我教啦！我細佬10歲都已經問我性問題啦，好正常 ，不是私人事。」<br />\n<br />\n談到網友負評如潮，更留言問她老公為何會娶她入門？Jinny說：「我的確是入了家門喎！大家開心就得啦！鍾意睇就睇，唔鍾意睇就不要睇囉！」她又寸寸貢說：「大家（指傳媒）最近都冇咩 做，咪當畀 大家寫囉！」如此「大恩大德」，未知各大傳媒要否向Jinny道謝呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d5ogXD89iaK0kkb1yoTBfQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjY3O2g9MTAwMDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D02c_ENP02P05070420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fd5ogXD89iaK0kkb1yoTBfQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjY3O2g9MTAwMDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD02c_ENP02P05070420.jpg&h=e86d18bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%90%B3%E8%8B%A5%E5%B8%8C%E7%88%86%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%AD%BB%E6%92%90%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8-220404704.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%25B8%258C%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B8%25B8-220404704.html&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=497b1a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%90%B3%E8%8B%A5%E5%B8%8C%E7%88%86%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%AD%BB%E6%92%90%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8-220404704.html</a>"},{"pid":"b479c766953c8b79f53285a2c4ec547019e23a84","tid":1961711,"u